                                </td>
                            </tr>

                            <tr>
                                <td>
                                    General Practice Data Manager
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Compiles and prepares the list of exempt practices to send the secure link via email</li>
                                        <li>Manages the json files from exempt practices AND prepares the AIHW report for each PHN in csv format</li>
