                                    </ul>
                                </td>
                            </tr>

                            <tr>
                                <td>
                                    General Practice Data Team Member
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Generating the PIPQI AIHW report which is used in combination with the json files</li>                                        
                                        <li>Validation of the csv file submitted to the Department of Human Services</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </td>
                            </tr>

                            <tr>
                                <td>
                                    General Practice Data Administrator
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Managing, tracking practice’s signed DSA through DocuSign</li>
                                        <li>Ensuring compliant practices are onboarded</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </td>
                            </tr>

                            <tr>
                                <td>
                                    Senior Programmer
                                </td>
                                <td>
